:::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the history of the Express...
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100050706-->
::::::{{A|VO chapter0 7 himeko 119.ogg}} '''Himeko:''' The Astral Express was a tool created by Akivili the Trailblaze, who used it to transport THEMSELF and the Nameless across the galaxy. It is rumored that there are other vehicles like it, but the Express has no such records.
::::::{{A|VO chapter0 7 himeko 120.ogg}} '''Himeko:''' When I found the Express, its memory had been severely damaged, with much of its valuable information lost. All I know is that the Express is an Aspect of Creation built by Akivili themself, and used to travel the cosmos.
::::::{{A|VO chapter0 7 himeko 121.ogg}} '''Himeko:''' As for how it was built and how it was damaged, I do not have an answer.
:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About where the Express is headed...
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100050710-->
::::::{{A|VO chapter0 7 himeko 122.ogg}} '''Himeko:''' The Express is traveling on a route that the Trailblaze once embarked on. The names of some destinations have been lost, but the first and final stops were both at Pegana &mdash; Akivili's home world.
::::::{{A|VO chapter0 7 himeko 123.ogg}} '''Himeko:''' We speculate the Astral Express started its journey from Pegana, stopping at each destination along the way before returning there for its next journey. However, the appearance of the Stellarons has caused a delay at each stop.
:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the Express' source of power...
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100050713-->
::::::{{A|VO chapter0 7 himeko 124.ogg}} '''Himeko:''' There is a legend in the galaxy: The heart of Akivili themself lies in the core of the Astral Express, providing it with the power to travel between worlds. But I found no evidence of that aboard the Express.
::::::{{A|VO chapter0 7 himeko 125.ogg}} '''Himeko:''' Besides, the Express existed before the Trailblaze fell. There's no way they could have had two hearts, right? However, it is likely that the Express possesses some sort of mechanism to transfer power from the Trailblaze.
::::::{{A|VO chapter0 7 himeko 126.ogg}} '''Himeko:''' It wouldn't be possible with a normal Pathstrider.
:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
