::::::{{A|VO chapter0 7 himeko 127.ogg}} '''Himeko:''' The fallen Aeon, deceased Trailblaze &mdash; THEIR passing is still a mystery, but of all the known Aeons, Akivili was the closest to mankind.
::::::{{A|VO chapter0 7 himeko 128.ogg}} '''Himeko:''' In the databank aboard the Express, it is recorded that THEY walked among the mortals &mdash; adventuring, fighting, and celebrating with THEM. Although THEY were an Aeon restrained by the "Primum Mobile," Akivili enjoyed a freedom similar to us mortals.
